Title: An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Navarro in the City of Marawi to Barangay Datu Saber
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA BLG. 656
An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Navarro in the City of Marawi to Barangay Datu Saber
Section 1. The name of Barangay Navarro in the City of Marawi is changed to Barangay Datu Saber.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
